reviews.text:
So, going into this, based off the name alone, I am assuming this is going to use the amazing cream base from DAAPled pears. Just based off smell, I can’t quite figure out what was thrown at the cream base this time. It smells fruity and maybe like kiwi?&#xD;
&#xD;
Well, kiwi is definitely not in this mix. I’m almost positive it is honeydew, but I am not sure what else is in it. It is bright, full of flavor, and absolutely delicious. I really hope I have all the flavors to mix more of this, because I am already about half way through the bottle and I really don’t want it to be gone.&#xD;
&#xD;
This is probably the hardest review I’ve had to write for MC just because it is so good. I don’t really have anything to complain about. Looking at the recipe, I’m surprised I couldn’t pick up on the lime. It does a brilliant job, paired with FA Aurora, of really boosting the flavor of the honeydew. Sorry this review is so short Fo, brilliant job.&#xD;
